0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"x:mx-auto x:flex x:max-w-(--nextra-content-width)","children":["$","$L2",null,{"value":[{"value":"Monorepo layout","id":"monorepo-layout","depth":2},{"value":"Web app data flow","id":"web-app-data-flow","depth":2},{"value":"Docs site","id":"docs-site","depth":2}],"children":[["$","$L3",null,{}],["$","$L4",null,{"metadata":{"title":"Architecture","filePath":"content/architecture.mdx"},"sourceCode":"---\ntitle: Architecture\n---\n\n# Architecture\n\nThis page is a stub. A deeper architecture overview will be added later.\n\n## Monorepo layout\n\n```text\napps/\n  web/    # Next.js 16 app (primary product, deployed to Vercel)\n  docs/   # Nextra docs site (this site, deployed as a separate Vercel project)\npackages/\n  # Shared packages will live here as the codebase grows.\n```\n\n## Web app data flow\n\n- **Auth** — Clerk, scoped via `auth()` on every server-side operation.\n- **Database** — Drizzle ORM against PostgreSQL on Neon.\n- **AI** — Vercel AI SDK + OpenAI (`gpt-4.1-nano`) for flashcard generation.\n\n## Docs site\n\nThe docs site is a stripped-down Next.js app powered by [Nextra](https://nextra.site/) and `nextra-theme-docs`. It does not import from `apps/web`; this keeps docs builds fast and deploys independent.","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"nextra-skip-nav"}],["$","main",null,{"data-pagefind-body":true,"children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-bold x:mt-2 x:text-4xl","children":["Architecture","$undefined"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":"This page is a stub. A deeper architecture overview will be added later."}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"monorepo-layout","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10 x:border-b x:pb-1 x:text-3xl nextra-border","children":["Monorepo layout",["$","$L5",null,{"id"